						                  Diaspora Banking

						               </div>
						               <p class="content-card-item__ellipsis">Enjoy personalized support through our Diaspora Banking services, including a dedicated Relationship Manager, tailored insurance cover for you and your family, and expert investment advice on local opportunities. You will also benefit from flexible mortgage financing in your preferred currency, making it easier to build or buy a home in Kenya.</p>

